---
permalink: "/_admin/index.html"
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="bg">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex,nofollow">
  <title>DK App Tools Админ панел</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #08090a;
      --panel: rgba(24, 26, 30, 0.94);
      --panel-soft: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.035);
      --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.09);
      --border-gold: rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.26);
      --gold: #d6a83d;
      --gold-light: #f0cf77;
      --text: #f4efe6;
      --muted: #aaa59a;
      --muted-2: #7f7a70;
      --green: #7bd88f;
      --blue: #8bb9ff;
      --warn: #f0cf77;
      --danger: #ff7a7a;
      --shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.38);
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.13), transparent 32rem),
        radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.07), transparent 32rem),
        linear-gradient(135deg, #070809, #111317 52%, #08090a);
    }

    body::before {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      opacity: 0.2;
      background-image: radial-gradient(rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.38) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 24px 24px;
      mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, black, transparent 86%);
    }

    button {
      font: inherit;
    }

    .shell {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 32px));
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 24px 0 44px;
    }

    .topbar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .mark {
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-gold);
      border-radius: 15px;
      color: var(--gold-light);
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.18), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.035));
      font-weight: 950;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      box-shadow: 0 16px 60px rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.12);
    }

    .brand-title {
      font-size: 17px;
      font-weight: 950;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .brand-subtitle {
      margin-top: 2px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .status-pills {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 9px 12px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: var(--muted);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.035);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 850;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .pill.green {
      border-color: rgba(123, 216, 143, 0.28);
      color: var(--green);
      background: rgba(123, 216, 143, 0.08);
    }

    .pill.gold {
      border-color: var(--border-gold);
      color: var(--gold-light);
      background: rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.09);
    }

    .intro {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .card {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(30, 33, 38, 0.94), rgba(18, 20, 23, 0.94));
      box-shadow: 0 22px 70px var(--shadow);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .intro-main {
      padding: 24px;
      border-color: var(--border-gold);
    }

    .kicker {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 950;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(32px, 4.7vw, 54px);
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -0.055em;
    }

    .lead {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 14px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .intro-side {
      padding: 22px;
    }

    .state-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .state-list li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 10px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .state-list strong {
      color: var(--text);
      text-align: right;
    }
.summary {
      padding: 16px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.032);
      min-height: 116px;
    }
.layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr;
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .rail {
      position: sticky;
      top: 16px;
      padding: 16px;
    }

    .rail-title {
      margin: 0 0 11px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 950;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .nav {
      display: grid;
      gap: 7px;
    }

    .nav-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 9px;
      padding: 11px;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      border-radius: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.018);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 850;
    }

    .nav-item.active {
      border-color: var(--border-gold);
      color: var(--gold-light);
      background: rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.1);
    }

    .nav-icon {
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      border-radius: 9px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .main {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .section-head {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .section h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 19px;
      letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    }

    .section p {
      margin: 6px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.55;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .button-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      justify-content: flex-end;
    }

    .button {
      border: 1px solid var(--border-gold);
      border-radius: 13px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      color: var(--gold-light);
      background: rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.08);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 950;
    }

    .button.secondary {
      border-color: var(--border);
      color: var(--muted);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.035);
    }

    .button[disabled] {
      opacity: 0.52;
      cursor: not-allowed;
      filter: grayscale(0.2);
    }

    .priority-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .priority {
      padding: 16px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.026);
    }

    .priority strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      font-size: 15px;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .priority span {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.48;
    }

    .split {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .row-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 9px;
    }

    .row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 13px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.024);
    }

    .row-title {
      color: var(--text);
      font-weight: 950;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .row-meta {
      margin-top: 3px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 6px 9px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: var(--gold-light);
      background: rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.12);
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 950;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .badge.green {
      color: var(--green);
      background: rgba(123, 216, 143, 0.08);
    }

    .badge.blue {
      color: var(--blue);
      background: rgba(139, 185, 255, 0.08);
    }

    .module-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .module {
      padding: 16px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.026);
      min-height: 130px;
    }

    .module-top {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .module-icon {
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      width: 34px;
      height: 34px;
      border-radius: 13px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      color: var(--gold-light);
      font-weight: 950;
    }

    .module h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 15px;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    }

    .module p {
      margin-top: 7px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .health-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 9px;
    }

    .health {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 12px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 15px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.024);
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .dot {
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--muted-2);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
      flex: 0 0 auto;
    }

    .dot.green {
      background: var(--green);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(123, 216, 143, 0.09);
    }

    .dot.warn {
      background: var(--warn);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.09);
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1040px) {
      .intro,
      .layout,
      .split {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
.rail {
        position: static;
      }

      .module-grid,
      .priority-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 680px) {
      .shell {
        width: min(100% - 22px, 1180px);
        padding-top: 16px;
      }

      .topbar,
      .section-head {
        align-items: flex-start;
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .status-pills,
      .button-row {
        justify-content: flex-start;
      }

      .intro-main,
      .intro-side,
      .section,
      .rail {
        padding: 17px;
        border-radius: 21px;
      }

      .module-grid,
      .priority-grid,
      .health-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .row {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    .admin-tabs-shell {
      align-items: start;
    }

    .admin-tab-button {
      width: 100%;
      border: 0;
      text-align: left;
      cursor: pointer;
      font: inherit;
    }

    .admin-tab-button:focus-visible {
      outline: 2px solid rgba(232, 195, 120, 0.9);
      outline-offset: 2px;
    }

    .admin-tab-button.is-active {
      border-color: rgba(232, 195, 120, 0.6);
      background: rgba(232, 195, 120, 0.12);
      color: #f8e5b7;
    }

    .admin-tab-panel {
      display: none;
    }

    .admin-tab-panel.is-active {
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .admin-panel-title {
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .admin-panel-title h2 {
      margin: 0 0 6px;
    }

    .admin-panel-title p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .admin-tabs-shell {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .sidebar nav {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 10px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="shell">
    <header class="topbar">
      <div class="brand">
        <div class="mark">DK</div>
        <div>
          <div class="brand-title">DK App Tools Админ панел</div>
</div>
      </div>

      <div class="status-pills">

      </div>
    </header>

<section class="layout admin-tabs-shell">
      <aside class="sidebar">
<nav aria-label="Админ раздели">
<button class="nav-item admin-tab-button is-active" type="button" data-admin-tab="articles" aria-selected="true"><span class="nav-icon">1</span>Статии</button>
          <button class="nav-item admin-tab-button" type="button" data-admin-tab="media" aria-selected="false"><span class="nav-icon">2</span>Визия и медия</button>
          <button class="nav-item admin-tab-button" type="button" data-admin-tab="apps" aria-selected="false"><span class="nav-icon">3</span>Приложения</button>
          <button class="nav-item admin-tab-button" type="button" data-admin-tab="support" aria-selected="false"><span class="nav-icon">4</span>Поддръжка</button>
          <button class="nav-item admin-tab-button" type="button" data-admin-tab="privacy" aria-selected="false"><span class="nav-icon">5</span>Поверителност</button>
          <button class="nav-item admin-tab-button" type="button" data-admin-tab="checks" aria-selected="false"><span class="nav-icon">6</span>Проверки</button>
          <button class="nav-item admin-tab-button" type="button" data-admin-tab="system" aria-selected="false"><span class="nav-icon">7</span>Система</button>
        </nav>
      </aside>

      <div class="content-stack">

                        <div class="admin-tab-panel is-active" data-admin-panel="articles">
          <section class="card section">
            <div class="section-head">
              <div>
                <h2>Статии</h2>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row-list">
              {% for article in collections.publishedArticles %}
                {% set adminArticle = adminArticles[article.fileSlug] %}
                <div class="row">
                  <div>
                    <div class="row-title">{{ article.data.title }}</div>
                    <div class="row-meta">
                      {{ article.url }}
                      {% if adminArticle %}
                        · Последна редакция: {{ adminArticle.lastEditedLabel }}
                        · Публикувана: {{ adminArticle.lastPublishedLabel }}
                      {% endif %}
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <a class="button secondary" href="https://dkapptools.com{{ article.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Отвори</a>
                </div>
              {% endfor %}
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>

                <div class="admin-tab-panel" data-admin-panel="media">
          <section class="split">
            <div class="card section">
              <div class="section-head">
                <div>
                  <h2>Правила за снимки</h2>
                  <p>Снимката трябва да е ясна, с правилно съотношение и разумна тежест, а не просто голяма като пиксели.</p>
                </div>
                <span class="badge">Само визуален изглед</span>
              </div>

              <div class="row-list">
                <div class="row">
                  <div>
                    <div class="row-title">Снимка за карта на статия</div>
                    <div class="row-meta">Препоръчително: 1600 x 900. Минимум: 1200 x 675. Съотношение: 16:9.</div>
                  </div>
                  <span class="badge blue">Карта</span>
                </div>

                <div class="row">
                  <div>
                    <div class="row-title">Снимка вътре в статия</div>
                    <div class="row-meta">Може да е с по-свободно съотношение, но трябва да е ясна и да има описание.</div>
                  </div>
                  <span class="badge blue">Статия</span>
                </div>

                <div class="row">
                  <div>
                    <div class="row-title">Снимки за страница на приложение</div>
                    <div class="row-meta">Използват се за функции, екранни снимки и продуктови секции.</div>
                  </div>
                  <span class="badge blue">Приложение</span>
                </div>

                <div class="row">
                  <div>
                    <div class="row-title">Тежест на файла</div>
                    <div class="row-meta">Голяма снимка може да се свие визуално, но тежкият файл пак забавя сайта.</div>
                  </div>
                  <span class="badge">Важно</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card section">
              <div class="section-head">
                <div>
                  <h2>Предупреждения</h2>
                  <p>Бъдещият редактор трябва да предупреждава преди неподходяща снимка да стигне до публичния сайт.</p>
                </div>
                <span class="badge blue">Планирано</span>
              </div>

              <div class="health-grid">
                <div class="health"><span>Снимката е достатъчно голяма</span><span class="dot green"></span></div>
                <div class="health"><span>Съотношението е подходящо</span><span class="dot green"></span></div>
                <div class="health"><span>Файлът не е прекалено тежък</span><span class="dot warn"></span></div>
                <div class="health"><span>Има описание на снимката</span><span class="dot green"></span></div>
                <div class="health"><span>Не се разтяга грозно</span><span class="dot green"></span></div>
                <div class="health"><span>Ясно е къде се използва</span><span class="dot green"></span></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="card section">
            <div class="section-head">
              <div>
                <h2>Как се показва</h2>
                <p>Голямата снимка може да се свие до размера на картата, но пропорциите трябва да се пазят.</p>
              </div>
              <span class="badge">Правило за визия</span>
            </div>

            <div class="row-list">
              <div class="row">
                <div>
                  <div class="row-title">Свиване без разтягане</div>
                  <div class="row-meta">Картата трябва да пази пропорциите. Ако трябва, снимката се изрязва красиво, а не се разтяга.</div>
                </div>
                <span class="badge green">Правилно</span>
              </div>

              <div class="row">
                <div>
                  <div class="row-title">Грешно съотношение</div>
                  <div class="row-meta">Вертикална или твърде широка снимка може да изглежда зле в 16:9 карта.</div>
                </div>
                <span class="badge">Внимание</span>
              </div>

              <div class="row">
                <div>
                  <div class="row-title">Прекалено тежък файл</div>
                  <div class="row-meta">Сайтът може да я покаже малка, но потребителят пак може да зарежда голям файл.</div>
                </div>
                <span class="badge">Внимание</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="card section">
            <div class="section-head">
              <div>
                <h2>Къде се използва</h2>
                <p>Една снимка трябва да има ясно предназначение, за да не се появява грешно в различни части на сайта.</p>
              </div>
              <span class="badge">Планирано</span>
            </div>

            <div class="row-list">
              <div class="row">
                <div>
                  <div class="row-title">Карта в списъка със статии</div>
                  <div class="row-meta">Малка публична карта. Тук лошото качество и грешното изрязване личат веднага.</div>
                </div>
                <span class="badge blue">Публично</span>
              </div>

              <div class="row">
                <div>
                  <div class="row-title">Вътре в статия</div>
                  <div class="row-meta">Изображение с описание, което подкрепя текста, без да доминира страницата.</div>
                </div>
                <span class="badge blue">Публично</span>
              </div>

              <div class="row">
                <div>
                  <div class="row-title">Страница на приложение</div>
                  <div class="row-meta">Изображения за функции, екранни снимки и бъдещи продуктови секции.</div>
                </div>
                <span class="badge blue">Продукт</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>

                <div class="admin-tab-panel" data-admin-panel="apps">
          <section class="split">
            <div class="card section">
              <div class="section-head">
                <div>
                  <h2>Приложения</h2>
                  <p>Управление на продуктови страници, статуси, линкове, функции и промени по версии.</p>
                </div>
                <span class="badge">Само визуален изглед</span>
              </div>

              <div class="row-list">
                <div class="row">
                  <div>
